Name: Exquisite Resonium Box
Desc: Get <color=#2BAD00>a random</color> A-Rank Resonium and have a 10% chance to get an additional A-Rank Resonium.
Desc2:
It's not a Resonia from a Bangboo merchant, but was picked up during exploration of a Hollow.
Bangboo merchants perform a simple appraisal before packaging them into different boxes based on their quality.
